{"url":"http://www.ratan.blog/wonder-woman","id":"http://www.ratan.blog/wonder-woman","title":"Thoughts on Wonder Woman","date_modified":"2023-01-02T01:45:01-05:00","date_published":"2017-07-04T15:11:46-04:00","content_html":"<p>So I joined my uncles, aunts and cousins when they went to see <em>Wonder Woman</em>.</p>\n\n<p>Speculation walking in</p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- Will this be any good? DC's recent track record made me pessimistic.  Some of my friends said this was good... but they were also OK with *Suicide Squad*.\">- Will this be any good? DC&rsquo;s recent track record made me pessimistic.  Some of my friends said this was good&hellip; but they were also OK with <em>Suicide Squad</em>.</span></p>\n\n<p>The pre-movie</p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- Trailers for *Atomic Blonde* and a *Blade Runner* remake were intriguing.\">- Trailers for <em>Atomic Blonde</em> and a <em>Blade Runner</em> remake were intriguing.</span>\n <span id=\"- Is it *Avatar 2: the Return*? No, it is Luc Besson's newest creation, *Valerian and The City of a Thousand Planets*. I was uninterested until I noticed Luc Besson's name on a poster.\">- Is it <em>Avatar 2: the Return</em>? No, it is Luc Besson&rsquo;s newest creation, <em>Valerian and The City of a Thousand Planets</em>. I was uninterested until I noticed Luc Besson&rsquo;s name on a poster.</span>\n <span id=\"- *Justice League* is already being advertised. At long last, I got to see the new, buff Aquaman in motion.\">- <em>Justice League</em> is already being advertised. At long last, I got to see the new, buff Aquaman in motion.</span></p>\n\n<p>The actual movie</p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- One of my cousins thought the flashback would end quickly and there would be a story in the present. *Nope*\">- One of my cousins thought the flashback would end quickly and there would be a story in the present. <em>Nope</em></span>\n <span id=\"- It's *beautifullllllllll*.\">- It&rsquo;s <em>beautifullllllllll</em>.</span>\n <span id=\"- Diana was born to fight.\">- Diana was born to fight.</span>\n <span id=\"- Will Diana jump off that cliff? Yes, but ...\">- Will Diana jump off that cliff? Yes, but &hellip;</span>\n <span id=\"- The eeriness of an all-female island wears off quickly. Once it was pointed out that there was only one child on the whole island things got a bit more disturbing IMO. Some of these Amazons are clearly older than others but ... none are children.\">- The eeriness of an all-female island wears off quickly. Once it was pointed out that there was only one child on the whole island things got a bit more disturbing IMO. Some of these Amazons are clearly older than others but &hellip; none are children.</span>\n <span id=\"- I guess sometime in this movie, we'll find out if the Greek Gods are canon in the DC Cinematic Universe. Question is, are the DC Greek Gods canon in the original mythology?\">- I guess sometime in this movie, we&rsquo;ll find out if the Greek Gods are canon in the DC Cinematic Universe. Question is, are the DC Greek Gods canon in the original mythology?</span>\n <span id=\"-\" title=\"War will never be fair!&quot; ... or something along those lines.)\n [- Will Diana jump off that cliff? Yes, but ...](id:- Will Diana jump off that cliff? Yes, but ...)\n [- It's not *beautifullllllllll*.](id:- It's not *beautifullllllllll*.)\n [- Is our male lead of this movie going to be a German pilot, in the service of Kaiser Wilhelm II's attempt to escape the encirclement of hostile foreign powers? That'd be a pretty interesting turn ... *Nope*](id:- Is our male lead of this movie going to be a German pilot, in the service of Kaiser Wilhelm II's attempt to escape the encirclement of hostile foreign powers? That'd be a pretty interesting turn ... *Nope*)\n [- Amazons vs. WWI Germans: very suspenseful. I'm glad neither side was totally curb-stomped.](id:- Amazons vs. WWI Germans: very suspenseful. I'm glad neither side was totally curb-stomped.)\n [- There a lot of things that must be very carefully spelled out in old-timey English.](id:- There a lot of things that must be very carefully spelled out in old-timey English.)\n [- Hey look, it's [Ludendorff](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erich_Ludendorff), an actual historical figure. Nice touch.](id:- Hey look, it's [Ludendorff](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erich_Ludendorff), an actual historical figure. Nice touch.)\n [- Also nice to see that the Ottoman Empire's existence and role in WWI is acknowledged... I guess?](id:- Also nice to see that the Ottoman Empire's existence and role in WWI is acknowledged... I guess?)\n [- Diana is *not* an Amazon? OK.](id:- Diana is *not* an Amazon? OK.)\n [- &quot;You let that little thing tell you what to do?&quot; Since that era, we've leveled up to letting server farms tell us what to do.](id:- &quot;You let that little thing tell you what to do?&quot; Since that era, we've leveled up to letting server farms tell us what to do.)\n [- Will Diana jump off that cliff? Yes, but it's a long jump.](id:- Will Diana jump off that cliff? Yes, but it's a long jump.)\n [- I was very closely watching the boat in the background during the heartfelt goodbye scene, waiting ... wondering ...](id:- I was very closely watching the boat in the background during the heartfelt goodbye scene, waiting ... wondering ...)\n [- There was no way we'd get through a movie featuring an all-woman civilization without a funny but awkward convo about marriage, relationships and ... sleeping together. So it's a good thing we got that out of the way early.](id:- There was no way we'd get through a movie featuring an all-woman civilization without a funny but awkward convo about marriage, relationships and ... sleeping together. So it's a good thing we got that out of the way early.)\n [- London is horrible.](id:- London is horrible.)\n [- &quot;Ohhh a baby!&quot; I find it easy to forget that Diana comes from a society without children.](id:- &quot;Ohhh a baby!&quot; I find it easy to forget that Diana comes from a society without children.)\n [- A whole movie starring the secretary would be enjoyable. OK, maybe a series of short films.](id:- A whole movie starring the secretary would be enjoyable. OK, maybe a series of short films.)\n [- Lots of fun, but innocent scenes here. Exactly the sort of thing *Suicide Squad* didn't have.](id:- Lots of fun, but innocent scenes here. Exactly the sort of thing *Suicide Squad* didn't have.)\n [- The patriarchal and command-chain-obsessed British military is something of an annoyance for Diana.](id:- The patriarchal and command-chain-obsessed British military is something of an annoyance for Diana.)\n [- Hey Ludendorff might be vile, but should he really be a cartoon villain? He's an actual historical figure after all.](id:- Hey Ludendorff might be vile, but should he really be a cartoon villain? He's an actual historical figure after all.)\n [- The attitude that soldiers were born to die offends Amazons as much as modern society.](id:- The attitude that soldiers were born to die offends Amazons as much as modern society.)\n [- Very fitting, having a rope to compel people to tell the truth while travelling with a spy.](id:- Very fitting, having a rope to compel people to tell the truth while travelling with a spy.)\n [- What a saavy old man.](id:- What a saavy old man.)\n [- War is hell.](id:- War is hell.)\n [- Token Native American is here. Also a sad Scot. And Sameer.](id:- Token Native American is here. Also a sad Scot. And Sameer.)\n [- &quot;May we get what we want.&quot; &quot;And may we get what we need.&quot; &quot;But may we never get what we deserve.&quot;](id:- &quot;May we get what we want.&quot; &quot;And may we get what we need.&quot; &quot;But may we never get what we deserve.\">- &ldquo;War will never be fair!&rdquo; &hellip; or something along those lines.</span>\n <span id=\"- Diana is naive, and incapable of seeing the big picture, but is powerful enough to survive nonetheless.\">- Diana is naive, and incapable of seeing the big picture, but is powerful enough to survive nonetheless.</span>\n <span id=\"- Diana is a one-woman demolition crew. And can throw tanks.\">- Diana is a one-woman demolition crew. And can throw tanks.</span>\n <span id=\"- Photo time!\">- Photo time!</span>\n <span id=\"- Token Native American believes in Greek Gods. Well... given the events of the past few days, why not, right?\">- Token Native American believes in Greek Gods. Well&hellip; given the events of the past few days, why not, right?</span>\n <span id=\"- Some of these Ludendorff scenes are entertaining (and grisly\">- Some of these Ludendorff scenes are entertaining (and grisly), but I could not bring myself to ignore the fact that there was an actual German military leader named Ludendorff.</span>, but I could not bring myself to ignore the fact that there was an actual German military leader named Ludendorff.)\n <span id=\"- Sameer is funny, even when he's pretending to be a servant to a cruel colonial master.\">- Sameer is funny, even when he&rsquo;s pretending to be a servant to a cruel colonial master.</span>\n <span id=\"- Hard to seduce someone when you keep glancing at your side chick.\">- Hard to seduce someone when you keep glancing at your side chick.</span>\n <span id=\"- Dancing with the figurative and/or literal God of War?\">- Dancing with the figurative and/or literal God of War?</span>\n <span id=\"- The chase begins.\">- The chase begins.</span>\n <span id=\"-\" title=\"What's that?&quot; &quot;The future.\">- &ldquo;What&rsquo;s that?&rdquo; &ldquo;The future.&rdquo;</span>\n <span id=\"- There's a pretty exciting fight. A fight *to the death*.\">- There&rsquo;s a pretty exciting fight. A fight <em>to the death</em>.</span>\n <span id=\"- This is a poignant ending for this arc. Unusual for a superhero movie. Maybe Diana will mow down a whole army at this point?\">- This is a poignant ending for this arc. Unusual for a superhero movie. Maybe Diana will mow down a whole army at this point?</span>\n <span id=\"- WHAT?\">- WHAT?</span>\n <span id=\"- Oh well, still a good ending.\">- Oh well, still a good ending.</span></p>\n\n<p>Parting thoughts</p>\n\n<p> <span id=\"- Pretty solid movie. Misses some chances to be unconventional.\">- Pretty solid movie. Misses some chances to be unconventional.</span>\n <span id=\"- I really liked the humor, simple though it was.\">- I really liked the humor, simple though it was.</span>\n <span id=\"- Also enjoyed the various settings in this movie. Much more interesting than the drab prisons and urban sprawl of *Suicide Squad*.\">- Also enjoyed the various settings in this movie. Much more interesting than the drab prisons and urban sprawl of <em>Suicide Squad</em>.</span>\n <span id=\"- Always appreciate the &quot;War is Hell&quot; message.\">- Always appreciate the &ldquo;War is Hell&rdquo; message.</span>\n <span id=\"- Look, Ludendorff was awful in real life, but this is just silly. This is like seeing a Robot Hitler or a Mutant Stalin who randomly kills subordinates.\">- Look, Ludendorff was awful in real life, but this is just silly. This is like seeing a Robot Hitler or a Mutant Stalin who randomly kills subordinates.</span>\n <span id=\"- I think chopping off one of the final scenes would make for a better movie. I prefer gods which act in mysterious ways, as opposed to leading a blatant (non\">- I think chopping off one of the final scenes would make for a better movie. I prefer gods which act in mysterious ways, as opposed to leading a blatant (non)existence. However these scenes are not bad.</span>existence. However these scenes are not bad.)\n <span id=\"- One of my cousins pointed out: *that* mustache does not fit *that* helmet. You'll know the ones.\">- One of my cousins pointed out: <em>that</em> mustache does not fit <em>that</em> helmet. You&rsquo;ll know the ones.</span></p>","attachments":[],"tags":["movies"],"_ratan_blog_class":""}
